### Proposed Resolution: Add an "OSS Contributor Mode" to codebase_navigation or create a dedicated variant. Key differences: read-only analysis (no infra access), contribution guidelines discovery (CONTRIBUTING.md), good-first-issue selection, local test setup without prod credentials, community norm discovery (Discord/GitHub Discussions/Matrix).
### Cross-Phase Impact: LOW — specialized use case. But codebase_navigation's claim to cover OSS contribution is currently hollow.

